{"tid":1609862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"根本就唔係心理關口問題","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:41:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T02:22:41.000Z","uid":245203,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"07449884a84dfc025355c47d358f79e4c8fad5e0","tid":1609862,"uid":245203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:41:17.000Z","msg":"係實力差距問題<br />\n<br />\n一係武器，玩家最高功嘅都只係掟酒，但其實你又有幾何見到啲酒可以對班畜牲有好大傷亡？其實我覺得啲酒真係可以用得好啲。另外喺近距離嘅武器都係唔夠班，所以好多玩家都唔敢衝前<br />\n<br />\n二係裝備，好多玩家都出唔齊裝，可能係怕中途俾人見到，所以好多都唔夠裝<br />\n<br />\n三係通訊，因為每次match game都會有唔同嘅玩家，所以喺通訊配合方面都做得好差，每次團戰都有前排啲坦衝，後面啲support唔知咩事加埋以上原因而無跟上去幫手<br />\n<br />\n利伸：我講緊係lol隻酒桶"},{"pid":"14c097777a40f9117e6552b61ba5444a70c60142","tid":1609862,"uid":272292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:42:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"24c9c5c1d44476d2d07aec1ce349730b4bfa0696","tid":1609862,"uid":245203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"7ff26309e8445b1e019fe93c90aa88ece2fcf900","tid":1609862,"uid":245203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14c097777a40f9117e6552b61ba5444a70c60142","tid":1609862,"uid":272292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:42:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:43:28.000Z","msg":"我自己一直都唔認同圍溫泉嘅行動"},{"pid":"eca15f53eaf6f6845d3c35d44490afd7f3fbfa7a","tid":1609862,"uid":245203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:43:39.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"f593909b453cccc884336d7dd1d56dbb488c1cc0","tid":1609862,"uid":245203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:43:52.000Z","msg":"大家打機都要改善下"},{"pid":"62d39eb7338f567f737bfc5c662ef0785df4390b","tid":1609862,"uid":245203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgm